    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "Purpose and scop",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "This magazine has been dedicated to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "MR. GEORGE ADAMSKI.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "Mr. Adamski launched the IGAP - International Get",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "Acquainted Program - in 1959, based on the philosophy",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "that people in all parts of the world should be given",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "the opportunity of knowing what is going on everywhere",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "in the field of flying saucers. His hope was that as",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "many as possible would discover the truth of the pre-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "sent age and turn to face the time to come - to learn",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "to accept, through conviction, the fact that we are all",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "citizens of the Cosmos and Children of the Cosmic Pow-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "er whose Laws run through the entire Cosmos. These",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "Laws we can learn to comprehend through study and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "understanding of the »Science of Life«, brought to our",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "attention by the presence of friendly visitors from other",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "worlds.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "The magazine is sent to civil and military authorities",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "all over the world, to leaders in the United Nations, in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "the Vatican, in scientific circles, and to Press, radio",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "and TV authorities.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "The purpose of this magazine is to bring to every-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "one, everywhere, news of events from all quarters of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "the globe in all its varied aspects. This means any news",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "that can possibly be of value in our endeavour to bring",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "to mankind an understanding of what is going on in our",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "world all the time. We shall try to detect any and every",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "move in the direction of that truth which we have acc-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "epted, but which is not yet officially accepted or rec-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "ognized in broader circles:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "1. People from other worlds in our system are visit-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "ing our planet.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "2. People from other worlds are in contact with cer-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "tain political and scientific circles in East and West.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "3. People from all walks of life, official and unoffi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "cial, all over the world, have been contacted by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "people from other worlds; such contacts have been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "kept secret so far.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "4. The philosophy brought to the world by Mr. Geo-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "rge Adamski is considered and aid helping us un-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "text": "cover the truth of our origin and our future destiny.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "The magazine will make no attempt whatsoever to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "text": "fight anyone, in spite of any action which might be laun-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "text": "ched against it. Only the truth, whatever its guise, will",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "text": "be brought to bear, to allow each to decide for himself",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "text": "what he can and will accept in this wonderful world on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "text": "his march forward to new experiences.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "text": "This magazine is non-political, non-religious, non-sec-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "text": "tarian and non-profit-making. We hope that you may",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "text": "profit from reading it, and that you will tell as many",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "text": "as possible about it, - especially if you find it of value.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "text": "Please write to us if you find it without value or if you",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "text": "have any suggestions or comments to make.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 113,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
